syn match dalvikDirective /\.end\s\+\(field\|subannotation\|annotation\|method\|array-data\)/
syn match dalvikDirective /\.end\s\+\(packed-switch\|sparse-switch\|parameter\|local\)/
syn match dalvikDirective /\.restart\s\+local/

